metadata.name: NO PAIN   NO GAIN
metadata.description:
When you are born, many things are predetermined for you and you do not have the right to choose and it is not approved by you.
You are a winner in adolescence/youth/middle age and old age or whenever you can understand your surroundings.
Because your pain and suffering starts from where you start to grow.
Your growth comes with a lot of pain.
You cannot achieve glory without suffering.
